===Etymology===
{{root|en|ine-pro|*lewh₃-}}
From {{inh|en|enm|ablucioun||cleansing of impurities}}, from {{der|en|fro|ablution}}, and its source, {{der|en|LL.|ablūtiō||a washing away}}, from {{m|la|abluō||wash away}}, from {{prefix|la|ab|t1=away|lavō||t2=wash|nocat=1}}<ref>{{R:CDOE|page=3}}</ref>.

